Antennae (
Figs. 1–2
) slender, scape and pedicel elongate, antennomeres III –VI compactly assembled and nearly cylindrical, not narrowing proximally or distally; antennomeres VII –XI forming sharply delimited and loosely assembled club, antennomeres VII –X distinctly narrowing both proximally and distally, antennomere XI only slightly longer than broad. All antennomeres covered with sparse long setae.

